                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-65-off365 t18041205-65-cd366"></join>, a pair of sheets, value 5 s. a blanket, value 1 s. and a flat iron, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18041205-65-victim787" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Wallis
                        <interp inst="t18041205-65-victim787" type="surname" value="Wallis"></interp>
