                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041205-65-defend785 t18041205-65-punish369"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Grose.</p>
